Np Bro's, My hot ass Neighbor is not finished yet, that is why i could only post the first 4 pages of the comic. The way Jab works is that he releases a page when it's done. I guess sometimes he publishes a few pages in a week. Other times it takes longer for them to come out.

You can have a look in the official forum/blog on jab's page for the releases of new pages.
http://www.jabcomix.com/blog/

They go up there in the form of a thumbnail as soon as they are ready.

As a matter of fact i see that page 5 is ready for My hot ass Neighbor 7, if i can find it i will post a link to it with good quality.

Glad you all liked the torrent :)
